    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Order containing five species in one family in the northern hemisphere. Characterized as foot-propelled diving birds with webbed feet and pointed bills.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
